article_title: UnitedHealth Will Expand To 11 New States On Obamacare Exchanges

article_metadata.description: UnitedHealth Group (UNH) confirmed plans to expand for 2016 into 11 additional states including California with private health insurance products on government exchanges under the Affordable Care Act. The nation’s largest insurer said it would also grow its presence in the 24 states it already has insurance products operating on exchanges. [...]
